alk.html</link><description>在“谈话”中，艾莉森·伍德·布鲁克斯（Alison Wood Brooks）矿山多年的数据以优化您的对话。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 10:00:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/29/books/review/alison-wood-brooks-talk.html</guid></item><item><title>4本新的历史小说书充满了丰富的地方感</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/28/books/review/new-historical-fiction.html</link><description>我们的专栏作家在四个出色的新版本上发行。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 16:32:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/28/books/review/new-historical-fiction.html</guid></item><item><title>找到您的下一本书</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2025/books/what-to-read-next.html</link><description>从书籍评论编辑中阅读选秀者，保证适合任何心情。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 16:26:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2025/books/what-to-read-next.html</guid></item><item><title>2024年的10本最佳书籍</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2024/12/03/books/best-books-2024.html</link><description>《纽约时报》书评的工作人员选择了当年的小说和非小说。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 14:21:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2024/12/03/books/best-books-2024.html</guid></item><item><title>现在要读的最好的惊悚片</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2025/books/thriller-books.html</link><description>无论您是寻找经典还是最新，最伟大的，都可以从这里开始。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 16:26:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2025/books/thriller-books.html</guid></item><item><title>读书俱乐部：让我们谈谈艾伦·霍林赫斯特（Alan Hollinghurst）的“我们的夜晚”</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/31/books/review/book-club-lets-talk-about-alan-hollinghursts-our-evenings.html</link><description>这部关于生活，爱情，挣扎和胜利的奇特英国缅甸演员的小说是我们一月份的读书俱乐部讨论的话题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 20:03:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/31/books/review/book-club-lets-talk-about-alan-hollinghursts-our-evenings.html</guid></item><it